textBox.richText: My name is Monica Martinez and I am the Biller for the Orthodontic Division at UCSF. I am a Bay Area native and currently reside in San Francisco. I have had the privilege of working and building up many dental practices for the past 15 years and hope to continue doing the same here. During my spare time I enjoy running, I volunteer walking dogs and at The Botanical Garden, love to travel, cook and see live music.
